						<!--cached-Tue, 22 Feb 2011 03:09:22 +0000-->Great presentation Steven.<br />
<br />
One thought - instead of dumping the unneeded rendered fat from the rib steak, why not use it as the saut medium for the home fries pommes frittes style?  Or, if not enough oil, mix it with the olive oil.<br />
