					<div class='post entry-content '>
						<!--cached-Tue, 22 Feb 2011 03:09:22 +0000-->If anything, this method keeps the sub-surface layer in better shape than high-heat blasting methods. But to clarify, the steak is not cooked for 45 minutes. It's cooked for 10 minutes on a side. Prior to that the edge fat is rendered for 10 minutes. And at the end it's allowed to rest for 15 minutes.
						
